{"title":"在野火烧过的草地","authors":["张洪波"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在野火烧过的草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张洪波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不会想到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片温柔多情的草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无影无踪　无声无息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁制造了这样一次火葬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞去了绿色的青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风推动浑浊的草灰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我面前宣读一张张黑色讣告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头蜷缩在黑色的墓场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭干了眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟儿丢下用羽毛制作的纸钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依难舍地不肯飞向远方……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命运在暴跳的灾难中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂在无情的焚烧中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化为沉寂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我垂首在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站成了一块心事重重的碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然　我发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下竟然还有一棵幸存的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我惊奇——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它如一面飘扬的旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在呼唤生命的回归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦　既然死亡无法抗拒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么　生存也必然会信心百倍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对草的遗族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我终于相信了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活着的意义"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}